ign: center;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Payments</font></span></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"4\">Payments are processed by eBay on our behalf.</font></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Postage &amp; Packaging</font></span></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"4\">I Post all UK Orders out Free of Charge via 2nd Class Mail - Upgrades to First Class/First Class Recorded &amp; Next Day Special Delivery are also available. I dispatch All Orders the Same Day (Monday-Saturday). I also Post Internationally &amp; can ship this Item Worldwide via&nbsp;Intentional&nbsp;Tracked Mail, All Postage is&nbsp;quoted&nbsp;above - I charge postage per Order and not per Item. I ship all items in Hard Backed \"Do Not Bend\" Envelopes to avoid your photos getting bent by Postman Pat.</font></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Duplicate/Multiple Items</font></span></u></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Every photo is individually hand signed but&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">from time to time I have<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>duplicates/multiples<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>of the same item,&nbsp;if this is the\ncase&nbsp;you will see an option for multiple&nbsp;purchases&nbsp;above\nthe price.<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>All<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>duplicate photos will be the\nsame&nbsp;image as shown, just<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>signed\nin a slightly different place,<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>sometimes in a different area of the<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>photo,<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>but most&nbsp;signatures will be<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>almost identical &amp; you will probably not even\nsee the difference! Please rest assured that the item you buy today will be\n100% Authentic &amp; Hand Signed - I don't sell anything else!</span></font></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><u><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">Combined Postage</span></u></font></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"Arial\">With my&nbsp;superb combined postage offer&nbsp;it may be\nworth you taking&nbsp;a few minutes to browse My eBay Shop</font><font size=\"4\" face=\"Arial\">,&nbsp;I have<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>hundreds of similar signed items,\nall<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>competitively\npriced. I can send&nbsp;any number<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>of items you buy&nbsp;all\nin one envelope<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>for\nonly<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>one<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>postage cost (This includes International Orders - Standard\nUK postage is also FREE).</font></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><font size=\"5\">&gt;&gt;&gt;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://stores.ebay.co.uk/klhautographs\">CLICK HERE TO\nENTER MY SHOP</a>&nbsp;&lt;&lt;&lt;</font><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><font face=\"Arial\">&nbsp;</font></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><font face=\"Arial\">A Little bit about me...<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Welcome to my autograph page. I am Kim and I am from Manchester,\nEngland. I started collecting Autographs around about Summer 1999. I have been\na keen collector ever since my friend got me Paul Daniels and Debbie McGee's\nautographs in Blackpool in early 1999. Since then I have been addicted! I am\nprimarily a collector but a couple of years back I started swapping and selling\na few duplicates I had, I had such great feedback that I carried on selling and\nsupplying many other collectors. I opened this account to share my collection\nwith the World and now I sell autographs full time! I am so lucky I can do my\npassion as a job! I hope you can find the time to have a look at my complete\ncollection, I am sure if you are a collector, like me, you will find something of\ninterest!</font></span></p></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font